				"string" : "My word is certainly not the be-all-end-all here. I’m sure you will encounter bumps and roadblocks I haven’t discussed or thought of, and sometimes it can help hire a professional who can help you develop a solid SSDLC (I know a guy, hint hint). But you don’t always need to. If you have a simple enough threat landscape and technology ecosystem, you can hopefully implement  a SSDLC yourself without any issues, and profit from it. And hopefully this post and [my little template](https://gist.github.com/hellerve/80dec6ca52d9e207a3d1f95800ccdba0) can help you with it!"
